title: Cheap Trick - One On One [320k MP3]
description:
One on One is Cheap Trick's sixth studio album, and seventh release in general. Produced by Roy Thomas Baker, it was released in 1982 via Epic Records and was the first Cheap Trick album to feature new bassist Jon Brant.
